						               													<description>Cry Havoc! Is a free, mini-expansion for Cadwallon: City of Thieves. It features advanced rules and new Equipment cards to make combat even more interesting. In order to use the new Equipment you will also need to download The Inn expansion. The Inn explains how to utilize these new cards.&amp;#10;Cry Havoc! introduces weapons, traps, and spells that stun or wound player characters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This mini-expansion add yet another twist to how ducats can be claimed. Players now have the option of racing to collect ritual items for the Gods of Cadwallon, and with a bit of luck, earning wealth and even victory! However, beware of the risk it burdens ,as it might just kill off 1 of your gang members....Are you brave enough to venture into the ritual chamber ?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Another main feature of the expansion is the new combat system! Tired of normal hitting each other and moving the other ? Well now you get to stun and wound your enemies, causing them to lose precious time and action points ! This expansion takes the fight in Cadwallon to a whole new level !&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
